| Device ID | Device Category | Device Name | Mgmt IP/Hostname | Location | Model_OS_Version | Role | Owner Name | Owner Email | Owner Phone | Current Access Method | Allow MSSP Remote Access | Authorized Access Level | Allowed Operations | Access Methods Allowed | Authentication Method | Credential Vault Path | Access Source Restriction | Jump Host IPs | MFA Required | Session Recording Required | Backup Config Location | Audit Log Retention Days | SecurityOps | Log Type | Log Collection Endpoint | Log Protocol | Log Format | Log Retention Days | Notes |
